milestones.description: Hansie Cronje and Callaghan's 149-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 145 between Hansie Cronje and Andrew Hudson
Callaghan has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (100) in an innings in ODIs for SA, going past Hansie Cronje's 50
This is the highest match aggregate (547) involving teams South Africa & New Zealand in ODIs
Callaghan's 169 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SA), surpassing Gary Kirsten's 112
